blockquote>入親AO都係神科人 dse狀元/狀元爆星咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該冇咁誇..."},{"pid":"2fbd3f6ba6e62f0151744523980f92ebe5645975","tid":408984,"uid":34868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T00:40:53.000Z","msg":"jre點準備好? <br />\n睇legco野?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5bf5b4ff9482a36c2f358212a5161c6ad4ed65d","tid":408984,"uid":36143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T00:51:24.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"e3fd1dbe764ab023081e33580f7fe320d80429ac","tid":408984,"uid":85005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T02:14:54.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"186806ac67f007232d097778ba5dd2a0ebf41047","tid":408984,"uid":108244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T04:57:47.000Z","msg":"真心想知jre點做<br />\n中文卷就識寫<br />\n但英文卷係咪唔洗用曬data file 既野而寫一篇完整既文出黎？<br />\n即係例如一篇文要寫10個points , 係咪寫6個points and well organized 就合格到？"},{"pid":"3a2099a684d139453b65a293c4cae15b75ea0da4","tid":408984,"uid":65109,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:22:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真心想知jre點做<br />\n中文卷就識寫<br />\n但英文卷係咪唔洗用曬data file 既野而寫一篇完整既文出黎？<br />\n即係例如一篇文要寫10個points , 係咪寫6個points and well organized 就合格到？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nJRE係考你入到政府識唔識運用中英文、邏輯思考/judgement得唔得，係實戰<br />\n如果你以為好似中學雞咁有marking scheme，寫到個point就有分，我都幾肯定你唔會pass"},{"pid":"9a00ece31f9fa2d666f210e0680df5e61bb28abd","tid":408984,"uid":129393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:41:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真心想知jre點做<br />\n中文卷就識寫<br />\n但英文卷係咪唔洗用曬data file 既野而寫一篇完整既文出黎？<br />\n即係例如一篇文要寫10個points , 係咪寫6個points and well organized 就合格到？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nJRE係考你入到政府識唔識運用中英文、邏輯思考/judgement得唔得，係實戰<br />\n如果你以為好似中學雞咁有marking scheme，寫到個point就有分，我都幾肯定你唔會pass</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> hello grade member"},{"pid":"767ebe5550444bc5db304db0c664911b3d9bfa7c","tid":408984,"uid":129393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:52:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真心想知jre點做<br />\n中文卷就識寫<br />\n但英文卷係咪唔洗用曬data file 既野而寫一篇完整既文出黎？<br />\n即係例如一篇文要寫10個points , 係咪寫6個points and well organized 就合格到？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n簡單啲講，其實等於考你作議論文。冇固定畀分位，係成個邏輯同演繹咁睇。"},{"pid":"1f02f31a8cd40af8423a140399e221cd51ae0816","tid":408984,"uid":65109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:51:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>真心想知jre點做<br />\n中文卷就識寫<br />\n但英文卷係咪唔洗用曬data file 既野而寫一篇完整既文出黎？<br />\n即係例如一篇文要寫10個points , 係咪寫6個points and well organized 就合格到？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nJRE係考你入到政府識唔識運用中英文、邏輯思考/judgement得唔得，係實戰<br />\n如果你以為好似中學雞咁有marking scheme，寫到個point就有分，我都幾肯定你唔會pass</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> hello grade member</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24a878c48b29873d79cd27d5f97486ac73727c5b","tid":408984,"uid":77917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T09:44:02.000Z","msg":"strong post leave name"},{"pid":"2f81856e5be6876c55638d2a75823ec6ecb36e2f","tid":408984,"uid":77917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T10:04:42.000Z","msg":"iknownothing巴打，<br />\n你當年係點樣準備JRE呢?<br />\n自己本身有睇開中英文報紙習慣，但係感覺上唔係好有幫助，訓練唔到多角度思考，唔熟識從唔同持份者視角入手去分析一個事件，點樣可以係呢方面有進步?<br />\n另外睇D咩reading materials會比較有得益呢?<br />\n感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9c156936dc71197b390448cf1e1c3ba489e62b2","tid":408984,"uid":47112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T10:13:17.000Z","msg":"樓主分享下平時睇開咩書"},{"pid":"63598900f45d6b318a4cb67b89b8ae5ac5beccb4","tid":408984,"uid":129393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T10:24:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主分享下平時睇開咩書</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有人竟然對呢個有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過其實我睇嘅書同考AO完全冇關係<br />\n<br />\n乘機宣導一下：《三體》好好睇，科幻書來"},{"pid":"afb40009cd264bc433497a19468c472bb333ef41","tid":408984,"uid":108244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T11:28:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真心想知jre點做<br />\n中文卷就識寫<br />\n但英文卷係咪唔洗用曬data file 既野而寫一篇完整既文出黎？<br />\n即係例如一篇文要寫10個points , 係咪寫6個points and well organized 就合格到？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n簡單啲講，其實等於考你作議論文。冇固定畀分位，係成個邏輯同演繹咁睇。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以中文卷我覺得做得ok，但英文卷我上年考既時候都預左1.5hr做，但就睇得好慢/唔知d data file 係咪樣樣都有用/要寫出黎<br />\n<br />\n同埋都想問係咪一定要參考consultation paper , 即係要寫purpose , background 咁樣寫篇野出黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fe25096d56901453b9de7e87b3e6e0a4d345081","tid":408984,"uid":36143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:05:24.000Z","msg":"想問有無啲類緊既exercise 做？<br />\n例如 cre 似Sat <br />\napp test 似 GMAT<br />\njre似a lv?"},{"pid":"f698c195a777ebb5618c8c8f365546ff60c2c449","tid":408984,"uid":36143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:15:51.000Z","msg":"樓主呢"},{"pid":"a073939d8eb38348a69c3fb3acd749e78afa106d","tid":408984,"uid":106967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T08:03:26.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"f8c985a4179de16a844b77cb50484b9e853d3f10","tid":408984,"uid":143840,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T08:05:29.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"4933fd3d3c64093772b412b73e273e99e97f4907","tid":408984,"uid":75140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T08:22:52.000Z","msg":"想問樓主入AO既本地uni fresh grad大概係咩料子<br />\n三大神科？非三大有冇？<br />\n知唔知除左你呢屆外上一兩屆既大概料子係點"},{"pid":"a25112e86b8781ce58f61dc5c22e280503a7c752","tid":408984,"uid":21310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T10:34:20.000